flowchart TD
    A[Repo submission.py per problem] --> B[ClosedLoopRunner]
    B --> C[ensure_baseline or choose current best]
    C --> D["Write candidate workspace
    .agent-loop/problems/<problem>/candidates/<candidate-id>/"]

    D --> D1[submission.py]
    D --> D2[context.json]
    D --> D3[mutator.command.txt]
    D --> D4[mutator.stdout.txt and mutator.stderr.txt]

    D2 --> E[kernel_mutator.py]
    K2 --> E
    E --> F[New candidate submission.py]
    F --> G["popcorn-cli submit
    mode = benchmark or leaderboard"]
    G --> H[Kernelbot on MI355X]
    H --> I[Raw result artifacts]

    I --> I1["evaluation/result.txt"]
    I --> I2["evaluation/stdout.txt"]
    I --> I3["evaluation/stderr.txt"]
    I --> I4["evaluation/parsed_metrics.json"]
    I --> I5["evaluation/critique.json"]

    I --> J[evaluator.py parses metrics]
    J --> K[runner.py records evaluation]
    K --> K1[".agent-loop/state.sqlite3"]
    K --> K2[".agent-loop/problems/<problem>/knowledge.json"]

    K --> L{Improved and valid?}
    L -- Yes --> M[promote candidate back into repo submission.py]
    L -- No --> N[keep as historical candidate]

    G --> O["If ranked run:
    .agent-loop/ranked/<problem>/<candidate-id>.txt"]

    subgraph Workspace[".agent-loop directory"]
        W1["state.sqlite3
        SQLite store for candidates and evaluations"]
        W2["problems/<problem>/candidates/<candidate-id>/
        per-candidate source and logs"]
        W3["problems/<problem>/knowledge.json
        rolling memory and critiques"]
        W4["ranked/<problem>/<candidate-id>.txt
        saved leaderboard output"]
    end

    K1 -. store .- W1
    D -. candidate files .- W2
    K2 -. memory .- W3
    O -. ranked results .- W4
